name: Campfire
note:
Note that we set the evasion rate to 100%
This is because in the plugin parameters
we're using evasion rate for the move
resist state. We don't want this enemy
to be able to be moved

<AIType:none>
<noPopup>
<noHpBar>

We're going to give this enemy some custom
AI with eventing. So first we'll add an
ondeath tag to turn on a self switch
then the dontErase tag so the event can
keep running even if it's dead. The rest
of the AI is inside the events page.

<onDeath>
this.setSelfSwitch('A', true);
</onDeath>
<dontErase>
